						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">Quietust wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent"><div class="quotetitle">beneficii wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">You also have to set $2006 as well to your current nametable.</div><br /><br />No you don't - when you want to set your current nametable for rendering, you write to $2000 and specify your desired nametable in the bottom 2 bits (do this along with the reading $2002 and writing $2005 stuff).</div>
